@Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5029
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/liveness
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check - Readiness
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/readiness
Accept: application/json

###

### OpenAPI Specification
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Scalar API Documentation
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/scalar

###

### Create Purchase Order
POST {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/v1/purchase-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierID": 1,
  "orderID": 100,
  "currencyID": 1,
  "orderType": "ExternalPO",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-12-31",
  "whtRate": 3.0,
  "customerPO": "CUST-PO-001",
  "notes": "Test purchase order",
  "shippingAddress": {
    "contactName": "John Doe",
    "addressLine1": "123 Main St",
    "city": "Bangkok",
    "postalCode": "10110",
    "country": "Thailand"
  }
}

###

### Get Purchase Order by ID
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/v1/purchase-orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Purchase Orders
GET {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/v1/purchase-orders?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDirection=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Purchase Order
PUT {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/v1/purchase-orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rowVersion": "AAAAAAAAAAA=",
  "whtRate": 5.0,
  "notes": "Updated notes"
}

###

### Cancel Purchase Order
POST {{Maliev.PurchaseOrderService.Api_HostAddress}}/purchase-orders/v1/purchase-orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
